(3, 'Vitamins', 'Acidophilus Probiotic Blend', 20.00, 'assets/img/vitamins/v5.png', '2020-03-28 11:08:57', 'Follow all directions on the product package. Refer to the label directions for your specific product to see if the dose should be swallowed whole, chewed, sprinkled onto food or mixed with liquid. If you have any questions, ask your doctor or pharmacist.\r\n\r\nSome probiotic products may contain live bacteria (such as bifidobacteria). Antibiotics may prevent these products from working well. Take any product containing live bacteria at least 2 to 3 hours before or after taking antibiotics. Follow the directions for your specific product.\r\n\r\nIf you are taking this product for diarrhea due to antibiotics, do not use it if you have a high fever or for more than 2 days, unless directed by your doctor. You may have a serious problem that requires medical treatment.\r\n\r\nIf your condition persists or worsens, or if you think you may have a serious medical problem, seek immediate medical attention.\r\nSide Effects\r\nAn increase in stomach gas or bloating may occur. If this effect persists or worsens, notify your doctor or pharmacist promptly.\r\n\r\nTell your doctor right away if any of these unlikely but serious side effects occur: signs of infection (such as high fever, chills, persistent cough).\r\n\r\nA very serious allergic reaction to this product is rare. However, seek immediate medical attention if you notice any of the following symptoms of a serious allergic reaction: rash, itching/swelling (especially of the face/tongue/throat), severe dizziness, trouble breathing.\r\n\r\nThis is not a complete list of possible side effects. If you notice other effects not listed above, contact your doctor or pharmacist.'),
(4, 'Sexual-Health', 'Fiesta Condoms', 8.00, 'assets/img/sex/s2.png', '2020-03-28 11:08:57', 'Fiesta condoms are birth control and contraceptives, effective in protecting against STD and STI like HIV (AIDS) and unplanned pregnancy.\r\n\r\nFiesta Condoms are made up of different variants to enhance all sexual needs. Fiesta provides pleasure and quality protection to both partners, leaving a lasting memory of a couple yearning for more.\r\n\r\nFiesta classic Fiesta classic condom has been gently lubricated to increase the pleasure for you and your partner. Your confidence and pleasure are guaranteed with Fiesta classic condoms. Fiesta dotted Fiesta dotted condom has more than 500 pleasure dots on the surface to increase stimulation for both partners.\r\n\r\nFiesta Condoms, \"She’ll want more!\"'),
